{"article_id":"mtibQjofi1QAtJwv","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"After a night of violent protests and looting , police in Charlotte tried to assuage outrage over Tuesday ' s fatal shooting of a black man by an officer ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"calling for calm Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"and saying","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that the version of events","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"leading up to the shooting","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"being cited by members of the public","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"was based on incorrect information .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Neighbors and a relative said","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"that Keith Lamont Scott was reading a book in his car","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"while he waited for his son to get off a school bus ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"but police said","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"the 43-year-old father had a gun","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"that he repeatedly refused to drop","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"when ordered by officers","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"and which was recovered at the scene of the shooting .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"\" It ' s time","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"to change the narrative ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"because I can tell you from the facts","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"that the story ' s a little bit different","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"as to how it ' s been portrayed so far , especially through social media , \"","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Charlotte-Mecklenburg Police Chief Kerr Putney said Wednesday during a news conference .","depth":4},{"id":21,"text":"Tuesday ' s police shooting of Mr. Scott and Friday ' s fatal shooting of an unarmed black man by a white police officer in Tulsa , Oklahoma , stoked racial tensions locally and nationally ,","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"drawing comments from the presidential nominees and the attention of the Justice Department .","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"Protests had been peaceful in Tulsa","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"but became destructive overnight Tuesday in Charlotte .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Sixteen police officers were injured","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"and businesses damaged and looted","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"when protests turned violent .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Violent protests began again after sundown in downtown Charlotte","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"as demonstrators rushed police in riot gear at a downtown hotel ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"forcing officers to fire multiple tear gas rounds at several sites .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Protesters threw some of the canisters back at the police , along with bottles and other debris .","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"SEE ALSO :","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"No racial bias in police shootings ,","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"study by Harvard professor shows","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"CNN reporter Ed Lavandera was tackled by a rioter","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"while doing a live feed and interview with host Anderson Cooper ;","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Mr. Lavandera later shrugged it off","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"by disparaging his attacker ' s football skills .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"The city of Charlotte said","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"one person had been shot in the head during the protests","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"and is on life support .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"But officials said","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"the shooting was civilian-on-civilian","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"and did not involve the police .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"At least one nearby store was looted ,","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"CNN ' s live footage showed .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"Videos of the fatal shooting of Terrence Crutcher in Tulsa have provided fodder","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"for his family","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"to publicly contest the version of events","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"described by police ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"who quickly released footage of the event","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"and do not dispute the fact","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"that Mr. Crutcher was unarmed .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"But it ' s unclear whether videos of Tuesday ' s shooting of Mr. Scott in Charlotte will soon become public .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"The black police officer","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"who opened fire on Mr. Scott","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"was not wearing a body camera ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"as Charlotte-Mecklenburg officers are required ,","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"but video from other officers ' body-worn or dashboard-mounted cameras may have captured the shooting .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"The North Carolina chapter of the American Civil Liberties Union is calling for the immediate release of the footage ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"stressing","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"that a new law","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"that will make it more difficult to release body camera footage","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"is set to take effect in less than two weeks .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"\" As we ' ve seen elsewhere ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"video footage of police shootings can provide crucial evidence of what took place -","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"especially when there are conflicting accounts from police and community members , \"","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"said Karen Anderson , executive director of North Carolina ' s ACLU .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"\" Charlotte should set an example for North Carolina","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"by releasing footage of the shooting promptly","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"before the obstacles","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"imposed by the new state law","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"take effect . \"","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"Police are reviewing multiple recordings from the scene .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"It ' s unclear whether there is video","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that captured the entire incident ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"which began","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"as officers responded to an apartment complex","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"to serve a warrant on a resident .","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"There officers encountered Mr. Scott ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"who","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"officials said","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"exited a vehicle with a handgun","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"and refused multiple commands","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"to drop the weapon","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"before Officer Brently Vinson opened fire .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"Chief Putney said Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"that the police department does not intend to release video of the shooting","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"until its investigation is complete .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"\" Right now , we can ' t release it , \"","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"the chief said ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"citing state law .","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"\" It would have a negative impact on the integrity of the case ,","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"and that ' s not something we are going to do . \"","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"Charlotte Mayor Jennifer Roberts ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"appearing on CNN Wednesday afternoon ,","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"she hopes","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"the video can be released \" as quickly as possible . \"","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"A woman","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"claiming to be Mr. Scott ' s daughter","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"said in a video","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"that was posted to Facebook","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"and widely shared","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"that her father was not armed","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"and was holding a book , not a gun ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"when he was shot .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"Civil rights activist John Barnett said Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"that he has spoken with a witness","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"who said","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"Mr. Scott did not make any threatening moves toward police","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"before he was shot .","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"Mr. Barnett warned","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"that ,","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"with different accounts of the events emerging ,","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"release of police videos might be necessary","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"to restore calm .","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"\" Just telling us","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"this is still under investigation","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"is not good enough for the windows of the Wal-Mart , \"","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"he said ,","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"referring to the retail store","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"that was looted","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"when protests turned violent overnight .","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"Chief Putney rebutted the claims","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"that Mr. Scott was carrying a book , not a gun ,","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"that officers did not recover a book from the scene","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"but had found a weapon .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"Video of police shootings has proven key to investigations of use of force in the past .","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"A South Carolina police officer was indicted earlier this year on federal charges","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"after bystander video showed him shooting an unarmed black man in the back","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"as he ran away after a traffic stop .","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"Tulsa police were quick to release video","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"capturing Friday ' s fatal shooting of Mr. Crutcher .","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"Videos from a dashboard camera and a helicopter","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"showing the fatal shooting of the unarmed black man","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"were released","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"just three days after he was killed .","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"The videos show Mr. Crutcher walking back to his vehicle","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"with his hands above his head","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"just before he is shot .","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"A lawyer for the white police officer","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"who opened fire ,","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"Betty Shelby , said","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"she fired","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"because she believed","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"Mr. Crutcher was reaching back into his vehicle for a weapon .","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"A vial of PCP was later recovered from Mr. Crutcher ' s car but no weapon ,","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"police said .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"Lawyers for Mr. Crutcher ' s family have used police videos","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"that captured the incident","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"to point out what they claim","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"is a flaw in the officer ' s account .","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"Attorney Benjamin Crump said","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"the images show","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"that the vehicle ' s window is closed","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"and smeared with blood .","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"\" He is not threatening to anyone , \"","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"Mr. Crump said .","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"\" How can he be reaching into the car","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"if the window is up","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"and there is blood on the glass ? \"","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"The Tulsa video has elicited reaction from the presidential nominees .","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"\" People","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"that choke ,","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"people","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"that do that ,","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"maybe they can ' t be doing what they ' re doing , \"","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"said Republican nominee Donald Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"referring to the officer","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"who opened fire .","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"Democratic nominee Hillary Clinton called the contents of the video \" unbearable . \"","depth":8},{"id":174,"text":"The Justice Department has opened a civil rights investigation into Mr. Crutcher ' s death in Tulsa ,","depth":7},{"id":175,"text":"and it is \" assessing \" Mr. Scott ' s death ,","depth":7},{"id":176,"text":"said Attorney General Loretta E. Lynch .","depth":6},{"id":177,"text":"\" These tragic incidents have once again left Americans with feelings of sorrow , anger and uncertainty , \"","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"she said Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"\" They have once again highlighted","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"- in the most vivid and painful terms -","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"the real divisions","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"that still persist in this nation between law enforcement and communities of color . \"","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"Ms. Lynch and other leaders urged","depth":7},{"id":184,"text":"those angered by the deaths to remain calm","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"as the incidents are investigated .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":371,"left":217,"right":370,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":206,"right":216,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":200,"right":205,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":200,"left":192,"right":199,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":192,"left":0,"right":191,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":1,"right":190,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":190,"left":2,"right":189,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":189,"left":188,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":188,"left":187,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":